                Post-War Aircraft Manufacture
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1943-04-06/debates/daa07347-e019-4ca2-9941-885e2c07d5a0/BusinessOfTheHouse(Scotland)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
